7 Section 1. R.S. 47:463.243 is hereby enacted to read as follows:
8 §463.243. Special prestige license plate; "Master Combat Infantryman"
9 A.(1) The secretary of the Department of Public Safety and Corrections
10 shall establish a special prestige motor vehicle license plate to be known as the
11 "Master Combat Infantryman" plate. The license plate shall be restricted to use
12 on passenger cars, pickup trucks, recreational vehicles, motorcycles, and vans.
13 (2) The Department of Public Safety and Corrections, office of motor
14 vehicles, shall create the special prestige license plate when the applicable
15 statutory provisions are met and the department's electronic vehicle and title
16 registration system is updated to accommodate the creation of new plates.
17 B. Provided the design is in compliance with R.S. 47:463(A)(3), the
